content: dorianjanezic: Merged two significant PRs this month: a bug fix for cached embeddings (#262) with substantial code changes (+1847/-1935 lines) and a new video generation plugin (#394) adding 406 lines of code. Currently has an open PR (#361) for an initial commit to komorebi. Activity was sporadic, contributing on only 4 days this month with a primary focus split between bug fixes and other work, primarily modifying code files.
